      {
        "id": 1,
        "english": "<span class='highlight1'>Daily</span> <span class='highlight5'>care</span> for <span class='highlight1'>mongrels</span>: <span class='highlight2'>Feed</span> the dogs <span class='highlight3'>at least</span> <span class='highlight4'>twice</span> a day (<span class='highlight5'>morning</span> and <span class='highlight1'>evening</span>). Always <span class='highlight2'>bring</span> <span class='highlight3'>water</span> and a <span class='highlight4'>leash</span> with you when going on <span class='highlight5'>walks</span>. <span class='highlight1'>Exercise</span> them twice a day for 30 <span class='highlight2'>minutes</span> each time. <span class='highlight3'>Prevent</span> <span class='highlight4'>fleas</span> and <span class='highlight5'>ticks</span> using <span class='highlight1'>special</span> <span class='highlight2'>sprays</span> or <span class='highlight3'>collars</span>.",
        "sentences": [
          "<span class='highlight1'>Daily</span> <span class='highlight5'>care</span> for <span class='highlight1'>mongrels</span>: <span class='highlight2'>Feed</span> the dogs <span class='highlight3'>at least</span> <span class='highlight4'>twice</span> a day (<span class='highlight5'>morning</span> and <span class='highlight1'>evening</span>).",
          "Always <span class='highlight2'>bring</span> <span class='highlight3'>water</span> and a <span class='highlight4'>leash</span> with you when going on <span class='highlight5'>walks</span>.",
          "<span class='highlight1'>Exercise</span> them twice a day for 30 <span class='highlight2'>minutes</span> each time.",
          "<span class='highlight3'>Prevent</span> <span class='highlight4'>fleas</span> and <span class='highlight5'>ticks</span> using <span class='highlight1'>special</span> <span class='highlight2'>sprays</span> or <span class='highlight3'>collars</span>."
        ],
        "translation": "🌐 日常照顧：每天至少餵狗兩次（早上和晚上）。散步時一定要帶水和牽繩。每天運動兩次，每次30分鐘。使用特殊噴劑或項圈預防跳蚤和壁蝨。",
