        "english": "<span class='highlight4'>Special</span> care for <span class='highlight5'>street</span> mongrels: Mongrels living on the street can have <span class='highlight1'>health</span> <span class='highlight2'>issues</span>. Always bring them to the vet for a <span class='highlight3'>check-up</span> first. These dogs are often <span class='highlight4'>scared</span> and <span class='highlight5'>shy</span> of humans. We need to be <span class='highlight1'>patient</span> and <span class='highlight2'>kind</span> with them. These dogs need <span class='highlight3'>extra</span> <span class='highlight4'>love</span> and care to feel <span class='highlight5'>safe</span>.",
